, 64, 64); text-decoration: underline;">Noah Smith broke it all down here</=
a><span>.</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; li=
ne-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Whether or not an economically weaker=
 China is a net-net &#8220;good thing&#8221; is up for interpretation. Coul=
d it make China more likely to provoke war? Could it weaken Xi&#8217;s/CCP&=
#8217;s grip on the population? Who are we to say. But, what we can say wit=
h some degree of certainty is that China&#8217;s economy is in a tough plac=
e while the US capitalist machine chugs along.</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64=
